# Build rules (binding for every change)

Full reference: `AGENTS.md` at the repo root. Summary below.

Stack: Next.js 16 App Router · React 19 · Tailwind v4 (CSS-first, tokens in
`src/app/globals.css` `@theme`, no `tailwind.config`) · shadcn/ui.

## Tokens — edit in `globals.css` `@theme`, never hardcode hex
- Colours (utilities `bg-/text-/border-…`): `forest` #083833 (dark bg / ink),
  `cream` #F9FAF5 (light bg / text-on-dark), `sage` #D9E9AA (accent/CTA),
  `olive` #50772F (mono labels / ring), `clay` `var(--accent-warm)` #c2683f
  (warm accent), `mist` #eef0e6 (education bg).
- Opacity via slash modifier (`text-cream/80`), not new `rgba()`.
- Fonts: `font-serif` Cormorant (headings/numbers/quotes), `font-sans` Manrope
  (body), `font-mono` JetBrains (kickers/labels/counters, uppercase + wide tracking).
- Headings: `text-[clamp(...)] leading-[1.0x] tracking-[-0.02em]`.

## Content
All copy & repeated data live in `src/lib/site-config.ts` (typed); map over it.
Don't inline card/step/testimonial lists in JSX.

## Components
Sections in `src/components/sections/` are **server components**. Only
`site-motion.tsx` and `src/hooks/*` are `"use client"`. Don't add `"use client"`
to a section without a real browser-API need.

## Motion — declarative `data-*` hooks, engine in `src/hooks/use-site-motion.ts`
`data-reveal` (stagger via `style={reveal(s)}`), `data-tilt` (base rotation via
`--tilt-base`), `data-px="n"` (parallax), `data-count`+`data-from/to/suffix`,
`data-grow-bar`+`--h`, `data-particles="id"`, `data-breathe`. Effects mutate the
DOM only — never drive them with React state. Always degrade under
`prefers-reduced-motion`. Use `cssVars()`/`reveal()` from `src/lib/css.ts` for
custom-property styles.

## New section checklist
Create server component with stable `id` + `data-screen-label` → copy in
`site-config.ts` → brand tokens + `data-reveal` → register in `page.tsx` →
add `id` to the light/dark lists in `use-site-motion.ts` → `npm run lint && npm run build`.
